							items: [
								{
									items: [
										{
											title: 'The INFINITY line in the concept <a href="#">product catalog</a>',
											fields: [
												"For professionals who love their craft for the endless possibilities of creativity and the look of delight in the client's eyes at the end of a challenging day, the Concept laboratory has created a unique range of products—the Infinity line."
											]
										},
										{
											title: 'We offer professionals a source of inspiration — find INFINITY in the catalog',
											fields: [
												"It is embodied in the dye palette, which contains 112 beautiful and on-trend colors."
											]
										},
									]
								},
								{
									items: [
										{
											title: 'Infinity concept — it always delivers a perfect result',
