										{
											title: 'We offer INFINITY concept hair cosmetics in a thoughtfully curated assortment',
											fields: [
												"Experts have developed an innovative capsule for salon use, a must-have tool for both beginner stylists and experienced professionals. INFINITY features only professional packaging formats with a bright, appealing, yet sleek and straightforward design. It includes graphical coding for categories, simplifying the stylist's work."
